    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is the perfect canvas for someone who loves to restore cars to their former glory. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a fantastic opportunity to own a classic model at an accessible price point. If you're looking for a budget-friendly fixer-upper with plenty of potential, this is the one for you!",
